PN,38202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784917111
OL,3,CFootage reveals moment Vickrum Digwa
OL,4,Ctells mother to take murder weapon
OL,6,FThe 53-year-old, of St Denys Road,
OL,7,FSouthampton, had been found guilty by
OL,8,Fjurors in May after taking the weapon
OL,9,Fback to the nearby family home on the
OL,10,Fnight of the murder on December 3 2025.
OL,12,FDigwa, 23, was jailed for life with a
OL,13,Fminimum term of 21 years on June 1 for
OL,14,Fthe murder of the 18-year-old finance
OL,15,Fstudent, after falsely claiming Mr
OL,16,FNowak had racially abused him.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
