PN,38203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784917111
OL,3,CFootage reveals moment Vickrum Digwa
OL,4,Ctells mother to take murder weapon
OL,6,FIn the video clip taken on Digwa's
OL,7,Fphone, which is pointed at the ground,
OL,8,Fhe can be heard speaking to Kaur in
OL,9,FPunjabi asking her to take away the
OL,10,Fweapon.
OL,12,FA transcript released by the CPS
OL,13,Fdetails how Digwa is speaking in
OL,14,FPunjabi and then said: "Take this",
OL,15,Fwhich they say was referring to the
OL,16,Fknife.
OL,26,@vD@XOUvD@bO]
