PN,38205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784917111
OL,3,CFootage reveals moment Vickrum Digwa
OL,4,Ctells mother to take murder weapon
OL,6,F"Instead, Kaur took the knife home and
OL,7,Fput it with a "larger collection of
OL,8,Fceremonial and other weapons in your
OL,9,Fson's bedroom", which would have
OL,10,Fhelped to conceal its use because she
OL,11,Fwanted him to "avoid being caught",
OL,12,Fthe judge said.
OL,14,FThe judge said her actions at Belmont
OL,15,FRoad before and after taking the
OL,16,Fdagger away "added to your son's
OL,17,Fpretence that he had done nothing
OL,18,Fwrong and that he was the victim".
OL,26,@nD@AO]oD@OOUqD@NO]sD@OOUsD@bO]xD@MOUzD@
OL,26,AaO]
