CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784917111
OL,3,CFootage reveals moment Vickrum Digwa
OL,4,Ctells mother to take murder weapon
OL,6,FThe statement added: "Our focus is on
OL,7,Fmaking sure the ongoing investigations
OL,8,Fleave no stone unturned as we fight
OL,9,Ffor the full truth about what happened
OL,10,Flast December, and we continue to urge
OL,11,Fthe Government to deliver the changes
OL,12,Four wonderful son deserves."
OL,14,FIn the wake of Digwa's case, anger
OL,15,Ferupted following the release of
OL,16,Fpolice body-worn video showing Mr
OL,17,FNowak, from Chafford Hundred in Essex,
OL,18,Fbeing placed in handcuffs moments
OL,19,Fbefore he became unconscious and
OL,20,Fsubsequently died.
OL,26,@nD@VOUtD@\O]
